* Audit Log\nSystem Table
** Location
***_ system.access.audit
***_ Configured at account level
***_ Applies to all workspaces
** Key columns
***_ event_time, event_date
***_ user_identity (email)
***_ workspace_id (0 = account-level)
***_ service_name, action_name
***_ request_params, response
***_ source_ip_address
** Retention
***_ Up to 1 year
***_ Plan external retention beyond 1 year
** Centralized
***_ Single table for all workspaces
***_ Simplifies compliance investigations
@endmindmap
